wiki.content: "Deli" is a single and the third track off Ice Spice's deluxe EP titled "Like..? (Deluxe)". The song is unapologetic and bold, with Ice Spice owning her sexualization without it owning her. She showcases her wealth, success and ability to attract. On July 7, 2023, Ice Spice made an appearance on Capital XTRA Breakfast with Robert & Shayna Marie, where she teased "Deli" when she was asked what her favorite New York song was. Two days later, on July 9th, she offered a preview of "Deli" on TikTok and proceeded to film the music video on July 14th. Read more on Last.fm.
